==Useful Info==
'''Oklob saplings''' are immature [[oklob plant]]s, not quite as durable as an adult, but still capable of dealing just as much [[acid]] damage. Although easier to kill, they are worth much less [[XP]]. They can be created by [[Fedhas]]' Overgrowth, and found in a few [[vault]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*See [[oklob plant]] for strategy.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.28]], Spit Acid dealt 3d7 base damage, but had an extra 4d5 "acid splash" on top of it.
*They could be summoned in [[Zot Defense]], before it was removed in [[0.16]].
